The paper deals with privacy issues related to location data, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses optimization problems and algorithms for constructing histograms, which could be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR), databases (cs.DB), and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper proposes privacy notions and algorithms for protecting sensitive information, which could be categorized under social and information networks (cs.SI).
